programme.</p><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span><a href="/meph/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">MEPH</a></span></h4><ul><li>MEPH — HVAC, power, lighting &amp; public health</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span><a href="/commercial/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Commercial Fit-out</a></span></h4><ul><li>Cat A &amp; Cat B fit-out &amp; refurbishment</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span><a href="/fabric/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Fabric</a></span></h4><ul><li>Cladding, roofing, render &amp; envelope</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span><a href="/groundworks/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Landscaping</a></span></h4><ul><li>Hard &amp; soft landscaping, surfacing, boundaries</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Areas we cover</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Crawley &amp; Gatwick &amp; the<br>surrounding area.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><span class="sector">Crawley</span><span class="sector">Gatwick</span><span class="sector">Manor Royal</span><span class="sector">Horley</span><span class="sector">Three Bridges</span><span class="sector">Ifield</span><span class="sector">Copthorne</span><span class="sector">Horsham</span><span class="sector">East Grinstead</span><span class="sector">Redhill</span><span class="sector">Reigate</span><span class="sector">Burgess Hill</span><span class="sector">Haywards Heath</span><span class="sector">Lingfield</span></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Why AMPM</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Local, accountable,<br>one team.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>On your doorstep</span></h4><ul><li><strong>Local base, fast response</strong> — our Burgess Hill office is minutes from Crawley and Gatwick, so we're quick to site and stay close throughout the job.</li><li><strong>Manor Royal &amp; airport-estate ready</strong> — we understand working in a busy business district and around an operational airport estate, with the access, security and out-of-hours constraints that come with it.</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span>One accountable team</span></h4><ul><li><strong>Industrial, logistics &amp; commercial covered</strong> — from warehouse and distribution units to offices and trade premises, we work across the building types this area is built on.</li><li><strong>One team, every trade</strong> — MEPH, commercial fit-out, fabric and external works self-delivered under one accountable team, so services, space and building hand over together.</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Crawley &amp; Gatwick questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Are you local to Crawley and Gatwick?</summary><p>Yes — about as local as it gets. Our office is in Burgess Hill, West Sussex, minutes from Crawley and the Gatwick estate, so we're fast to site and easy to reach throughout a project, not just at tender stage.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you work on the Manor Royal business district / Gatwick estate?</summary><p>Yes. Manor Royal and the airport estate are right on our doorstep, and the offices, industrial units and commercial premises across them are exactly the kind of work we self-deliver — MEPH, fit-out, fabric and external works under one team, with the access, security and out-of-hours arrangements these sites need.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you cover industrial and logistics units around Gatwick?</summary><p>Yes. The warehousing, distribution and light-industrial units around Gatwick are a core part of what we do — services, fabric and external works, in new and occupied buildings, delivered to AMPM Group's accreditations and the relevant UK standards.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top xlinks" data-xlink><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 22px;"><div class="kicker">Explore more</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Related across<br>AMPM Building&nbsp;Services.</h2></div><div class="xgroup reveal in"><span class="xlabel">Our service lines</span><div class="sectorrow"><a class="sector" href="/meph/">MEPH</a><a class="sector" href="/commercial/">Commercial Fit-out</a><a class="sector" href="/fabric/">Fabric &amp; Envelope</a><a class="sector" href="/groundworks/">Landscaping &amp; External Works</a></div></div><div class="xgroup reveal in"><span class="xlabel">Sectors we serve</span><div class="sectorrow"><a class="sector" href="/sectors/offices/">Commercial Offices</a><a class="sector" href="/sectors/healthcare/">Healthcare</a><a class="sector" href="/sectors/industrial/">Industrial &amp; Logistics</a><a class="sector" href="/sectors/residential/">Residential &amp; BTR</a><a class="sector" href="/sectors/">All sectors →</a></div></div><div class="xgroup reveal in"><span class="xlabel">Other areas</span><div class="sectorr